{"tid":174581,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"美國大公司小薯仔交流區","createTime":"2017-03-27T02:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T17:02:10.000Z","uid":96721,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90bec457a431945c20b746699e31fcb19e95d312","tid":174581,"uid":96721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:13:11.000Z","msg":"無聊開下 post 先<br />\n<br />\n呢度多唔多人係美國打工或者就快打工？可以係度吹下水<br />\n<br />\n我開個頭先<br />\n呢幾年係美國大公司打工，非常愉快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n福利同工作文化都比香港好好多，可能因為我係做設計方面，老細好睇重創意，而唔係你留係公司幾耐，所以只要出到貨，係唔會理你幾時返工放工既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知多唔多人係咁？"},{"pid":"ffe84ccb00d76fd18373219373492264f6655b93","tid":174581,"uid":92998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:20:05.000Z","msg":"巴打點解會係美國打工？係個邊讀完書留底？"},{"pid":"daca505c6e2b4628346ac479a25734154d3d2001","tid":174581,"uid":96721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打點解會係美國打工？係個邊讀完書留底？</blockquote><br />\n我係美國讀完 PhD 跟住就係度搵工啦<br />\n唔返香港啦"},{"pid":"849d97ca0231c489aefced68b7075e449321b9b1","tid":174581,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:47:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打點解會係美國打工？係個邊讀完書留底？</blockquote><br />\n我係美國讀完 PhD 跟住就係度搵工啦<br />\n唔返香港啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係直接用OPT搵工？"},{"pid":"592c396f895dbf8e0415aaceabfe3060ae26aa54","tid":174581,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"美孚撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34aa69c60aa1a43fa112d4ed2d05eb4596fa2f4","tid":174581,"uid":59516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T04:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打點解會係美國打工？係個邊讀完書留底？</blockquote><br />\n我係美國讀完 PhD 跟住就係度搵工啦<br />\n唔返香港啦</blockquote><br />\nPhD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2245122f7b4004ddf1796d1aaaf5998fbfef7c18","tid":174581,"uid":96721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T04:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打點解會係美國打工？係個邊讀完書留底？</blockquote><br />\n我係美國讀完 PhD 跟住就係度搵工啦<br />\n唔返香港啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係直接用OPT搵工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先 OPT，跟住 H-1B，再跟住綠咭<br />\n<br />\n搵工呢樣野好奇妙，識人好過識字<br />\n有人介紹搵工係易好多既，所以我都不斷嘗試介紹朋友入自己公司&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"a724d1028700439200e3b439870bf17eee512e2e","tid":174581,"uid":96721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T04:12:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打點解會係美國打工？係個邊讀完書留底？</blockquote><br />\n我係美國讀完 PhD 跟住就係度搵工啦<br />\n唔返香港啦</blockquote><br />\nPhD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我只係個小薯仔啦"},{"pid":"0baeadf39804072c6a6ecee3dcb9fba751370940","tid":174581,"uid":92998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打點解會係美國打工？係個邊讀完書留底？</blockquote><br />\n我係美國讀完 PhD 跟住就係度搵工啦<br />\n唔返香港啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係直接用OPT搵工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先 OPT，跟住 H-1B，再跟住綠咭<br />\n<br />\n搵工呢樣野好奇妙，識人好過識字<br />\n有人介紹搵工係易好多既，所以我都不斷嘗試介紹朋友入自己公司&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n巴打係做緊咩類型公司？<br />\n同事有無香港人 都係讀PhD留低定點?<br />\n想聽多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766c9c7e96cbdccfe28c2f1765f0d94b83f9d753","tid":174581,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:49:11.000Z","msg":"整game?"},{"pid":"1ecd9fa74a5f5459f233aac043d12a564d9a5edf","tid":174581,"uid":96721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打點解會係美國打工？係個邊讀完書留底？</blockquote><br />\n我係美國讀完 PhD 跟住就係度搵工啦<br />\n唔返香港啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係直接用OPT搵工？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先 OPT，跟住 H-1B，再跟住綠咭<br />\n<br />\n搵工呢樣野好奇妙，識人好過識字<br />\n有人介紹搵工係易好多既，所以我都不斷嘗試介紹朋友入自己公司&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n巴打係做緊咩類型公司？<br />\n同事有無香港人 都係讀PhD留低定點?<br />\n想聽多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遊戲設計<br />\n香港人唔多<br />\n其實公司連非美國人都唔多<br />\n工作環境算唔錯，好多時候要遲到早走，講聲就得，做得晒工作，無乜人理你幾時返工放工"},{"pid":"112e801210be9ad4ea71e42be6d586e00f5ca551","tid":174581,"uid":96721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整game?</blockquote><br />\n係！<br />\nOnline game company"},{"pid":"98e61406c36a91d5e955f7c812fa88f69ee6cae1","tid":174581,"uid":96677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>整game?</blockquote><br />\n係！<br />\nOnline game company</blockquote><br />\nGame呢行賺到痴線 識人oculus度做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465748aa4f017f36dd07c6602153895d74fb0890","tid":174581,"uid":96721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>整game?</blockquote><br />\n係！<br />\nOnline game company</blockquote><br />\nGame呢行賺到痴線 識人oculus度做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n捉到