.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a273f7dfe2a1d8a4bd22682599e53a5a95c38e4","tid":174581,"uid":10764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>College PT 做緊CVS cashier, 公司就大,薯仔都𣎴如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夠薯仔啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多唔多人係CVS買gift card? 其實係咪一定要check ID?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都多，一定要check ID,每人每日有個限額（好似係法例），我估怕人洗黑錢"},{"pid":"e4ad5d437ae0ac00854b32eba7fe31429abfd770","tid":174581,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好想全職整game<br />\n但做indie實在太困難...<br />\n香港又無乜依d機會</blockquote><br />\n我黎緊會全職indie整game<br />\n機會係要自己創做既<br />\n已搵到人搞左少少bgm"},{"pid":"95a5656baab5bd4f9bc7b3e0a470f17bf31da5bd","tid":174581,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:26:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家讀緊undergrad major Animation<br />\n5月要畢業啦<br />\n差唔多要開始搞opt<br />\n搵到工機會都幾微<br />\n係美國個電影同遊戲e行都好細 關係重要過一切<br />\n好多人都互相認識或者之前同一studio做過<br />\n比較唔信一個新人能力<br />\nBtw你公司請唔請人</blockquote><br />\n其實近年好多game都係indie公司製作<br />\n等老屎忽相信新人<br />\n倒不如自己創業"},{"pid":"2cfcf640ef805ab509cad7f4899334430cf5cdeb","tid":174581,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:29:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主如果岩岩畢業有興趣做game design 點入手好？<br />\n香港有邊間好少少既公司？<br />\n利申：有數學底</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知喎<br />\n不過係香港做，只怕會好辛苦&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n香港絕對無好既遊戲公司<br />\n要搞就自己搞<br />\n無老點你<br />\n靠香港依家既垃圾遊戲公司不如靠自己<br />\n<br />\n香港遊戲公司最出名係Madhead<br />\n出神魔之塔山寨日本隻P&amp;D<br />\n係出名整臭香港人個朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83c52ab5f66561422baccaabeb1a6c4f3e41640","tid":174581,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:32:02.000Z","msg":"入香港遊戲公司<br />\n人工唔會高<br />\n同時做多隻game OT做死你<br />\n賺得多錢都係老細賺<br />\n唔會似美國公司咁識得同員工分享成果"},{"pid":"9b80d8ef8d596a93c2caaeabfefd795b5375820a","tid":174581,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都好想全職整game<br />\n但做indie實在太困難...<br />\n香港又無乜依d機會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無打算去外國做？市場大過香港可能較易</blockquote><br />\n其實係香港搞<br />\n都可以做全球市場<br />\nApp Store, Play Store, Steam全部係面向全球既平台<br />\n<br />\n但重點係唔好咁老土又做武俠、三國個類題材<br />\n呢D題材認真難打入全球市場<br />\n如indie公司純做華人市場係好難賺大錢"},{"pid":"a4fa281cae9837d524a2232708ef6e94aae36dbd","tid":174581,"uid":104559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:23:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前係Bay Area做左年野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪IT？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2c3e21a3e98f07435ef8fd7088f59a9f52fd11","tid":174581,"uid":98112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:53:16.000Z","msg":"bio undergrad, 申請緊OPT.<br />\n<br />\n五月畢業，希望之後找到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28977c5446ab522ffb28a4037aee4476819fb48","tid":174581,"uid":96721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bio undergrad, 申請緊OPT.<br />\n<br />\n五月畢業，希望之後找到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想做乜？"},{"pid":"871677093a808c22bce0d7860c202a9011837d62","tid":174581,"uid":96721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都好想全職整game<br />\n但做indie實在太困難...<br />\n香港又無乜依d機會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無打算去外國做？市場大過香港可能較易</blockquote><br />\n其實係香港搞<br />\n都可以做全球市場<br />\nApp Store, Play Store, Steam全部係面向全球既平台<br />\n<br />\n但重點係唔好咁老土又做武俠、三國個類題材<br />\n呢D題材認真難打入全球市場<br />\n如<span style=\"color: red;\">indie公司純做華人市場係好難賺大錢</span></blockquote><br />\n紅字呢句唔完全同意<br />\n其實中國市場大得好緊要，只不過你要入去就一定要同騰訊一齊搞（同俾佢抽水），同埋大陸 copycat 太快太多<br />\n但如果以 indie 而言，你有個好新既意念，食到佢第一水都已經發左達"},{"pid":"c4b6b31365e02105f5a4896509dc038db3bc88fe","tid":174581,"uid":41314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"有冇entry level既mech eng既工介紹呀？<br />\n搵左好耐都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f059367cff5a5373016315cfe74087a64c42461","tid":174581,"uid":96721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:30:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇entry level既mech eng既工介紹呀？<br />\n搵左好耐都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係美國？<br />\n俾個 email 黎傾下：<br />\ngamershkg@gmail.com"},{"pid":"04d9e03c9af0471b03268203c4bef1e53b586d14","tid":174581,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都好想全職整game<br />\n但做indie實在太困難...<br />\n香港又無乜依d機會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無打算去外國做？市場大過香港可能較易</blockquote><br />\n其實係香港搞<br />\n都可以做全球市場<br />\nApp Store, Play Store, Steam全部係面向全球既平台<br />\n<br />\n但重點係唔好咁老土又做武俠、三國個類題材<br />\n呢D題材認真難打入全球市場<br />\n如<span style=\"color: red;\">indie公司純做華人市場係好難賺大錢</span></blockquote><br />\n紅字呢句唔完全同意<br />\n其實中國市場大得好緊要，只不過你要入去就一定要同騰訊一齊搞（同俾佢抽水），同埋大陸 copycat 太快太多<br />\n但如果以 indie 而言，你有個好新既意念，食到佢第一水都已經發左達</blockquote><br />\n做indie起碼窮3年<br />\n之後先再講有無機會追返平常人收入&hellip;"},{"pid":"fbce1ab1d53c4